"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-28-Top-tennis-players-return-to-Roland-Garros-for-2024-Summer-Olympics-1vBiFwDFCFi-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  The tennis events at the\\u00a02024 Paris Summer Olympics are taking place at Rolland Garros, the clay-court home of the French Open Grand Slam tournament, from July 26 to August 11. A total of seven players, including Zheng Qinwen and Zhang Zhizhen, will participate in the sport on behalf of China.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"